---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Tax Number (AFM) Greece | Taxomade">
  <main class="pt-32 pb-24 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-white">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <div class="mb-16 border-b border-slate-100 pb-12">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-6 tracking-tight">Get your Greek tax number (AFM) <span class="text-blue-800">—</span> fast and remote.</h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-slate-600 mb-8 max-w-3xl">The AFM is your gateway to living, working and banking in Greece. We register it for you.</p>
      <a href="/#configurator" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-lg font-bold rounded-lg text-white bg-slate-900 hover:bg-blue-800 transition-colors duration-200 shadow-sm">
        Get your AFM
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- What it is -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">What it is</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
        The AFM (Αριθμός Φορολογικού Μητρώου) is your Greek tax identification number. You need it for almost everything official in Greece: registering as a freelancer, opening a bank account, signing a rental contract, paying taxes, and applying for the 50% tax break. It's the first administrative step for anyone settling in Greece.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Requirements -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">Requirements</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-4 text-lg text-slate-700 list-disc list-inside">
        <li>A valid passport or ID.</li>
        <li>For EU citizens: no visa needed.</li>
        <li>For non-EU citizens: typically your residence permit / visa.</li>
        <li>A Greek address or a representative (we can act via power of attorney if you're not yet in Greece).</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <!-- How it works -->
    <section class="mb-16 bg-slate-50 p-8 md:p-10 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8">How it works</h2>

      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 flex items-center"><span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-slate-900 text-white flex items-center justify-center mr-3 text-sm">1</span> What you do</h3>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 ml-11">Send us a copy of your passport/ID and basic details, and sign a power of attorney so we can act for you.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 flex items-center"><span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-blue-800 text-white flex items-center justify-center mr-3 text-sm">2</span> What Taxomade does</h3>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 ml-11">Our licensed local partner registers your AFM with the Greek tax authority (AADE) on your behalf — often without you needing to appear in person. You receive your AFM ready to use.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <p class="text-slate-500 mt-8 text-sm italic">This is usually quick (a few days) and is the foundation for everything that follows.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8">FAQ</h2>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="border-b border-slate-200 pb-6">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Do EU citizens need an AFM?</h4>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-700">Yes, if they live, work or do financial transactions in Greece.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-b border-slate-200 pb-6">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Can I get it before moving?</h4>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-700">Yes — we can register it remotely via power of attorney.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-b border-slate-200 pb-6">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Is the AFM the same as registering as a freelancer?</h4>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-700">No — the AFM comes first; freelancer registration is a separate step we also handle.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Do I need it if I stay under 6 months?</h4>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-700">Often not for tax purposes, but you may still need it for banking or renting.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer Disclaimer -->
    <div class="mt-20 pt-8 border-t border-slate-200 text-sm text-slate-500">
      <p>Taxomade is not a government body. We coordinate licensed local accountants and lawyers. Information is general and not individual legal or tax advice.</p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
